  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Thomas_the_Threadbare\" title=\"Thomas the Threadbare\"><img alt=\"Thomas the Threadbare 2.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/Thomas_the_Threadbare_2.svg/50px-Thomas_the_Threadbare_2.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/Thomas_the_Threadbare_2.svg/75px-Thomas_the_Threadbare_2.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2d/Thomas_the_Threadbare_2.svg/100px-Thomas_the_Threadbare_2.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Ser</span><br />Thomas<br /><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> the Threadbare</span></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Thomas_the_Threadbare\" title=\"Thomas the Threadbare\"><img alt=\"Thomas the Threadbare 2.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/Thomas_the_Threadbare_2.svg/50px-Thomas_the_Threadbare_2.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/Thomas_the_Threadbare_2.svg/75px-Thomas_the_Threadbare_2.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2d/Thomas_the_Threadbare_2.svg/100px-Thomas_the_Threadbare_2.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap\">Personal arms</span></th><td>\nA frayed maunch, white on brown<sup id=\"cite_ref-Citadel_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Citadel-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><br />(<i>Brunâtre, a frayed-maunch argent</i>)</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Hedge_Knight_(comics)\" title=\"The Hedge Knight (comics)\">The Hedge Knight</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Thomas the Threadbare</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> during the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Daeron_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Daeron II Targaryen\">Daeron II Targaryen</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Thomas_the_Threadbare&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Thomas participated in the <a href=\"/index.php/Tourney_at_Ashford_Meadow\" title=\"Tourney at Ashford Meadow\">tourney at Ashford Meadow</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/209_AC\" title=\"209 AC\">209&#160;AC</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rthk_.5B.5Bthe_hedge_knight_.28comics.29.7Cgraphic_novel.5D.5D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rthk_.5B.5Bthe_hedge_knight_.28comics.29.7Cgraphic_novel.5D.5D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> His shield displayed a frayed maunch, white on brown.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Citadel_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Citadel-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Thomas_the_Threadbare&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Citadel-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Citadel_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Citadel_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.westeros.org/Citadel/Heraldry/Other/1/\">The Citadel - Heraldry: Houseless hedge knights</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rthk_.5B.5Bthe_hedge_knight_.28comics.29.7Cgraphic_novel.5D.5D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rthk_.5B.5Bthe_hedge_knight_.28comics.29.7Cgraphic_novel.5D.5D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Hedge_Knight\" title=\"The Hedge Knight\">The Hedge Knight</a></i>,  <a href=\"/index.php/The_Hedge_Knight_(comics)\" title=\"The Hedge Knight (comics)\">Graphic Novel</a>.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403094321\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.067 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.258 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 411/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10497/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 6345/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 660/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1287/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.170/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.34 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  249.773      1 -total\n 95.88%  239.473      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 95.42%  238.325      1 Template:Infobox\n 10.87%   27.151     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  2.53%    6.310      2 Template:Infobox_label\n  1.75%    4.373      1 Template:Date\n  1.42%    3.543      1 Template:Ref\n  0.93%    2.329      1 Temp